@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
actor Maker
actor Taker
rectangle "escrow\n(PDA, state)" as Escrow
rectangle "vault\n(PDA, ATA)" as Vault
Maker --> Escrow : opens, sets terms
Escrow --> Vault : holds the locked stake
Maker ..> Vault : deposits mint_a
Taker ..> Maker : pays mint_b
@enduml
